version_description: Basically these chords work on piano, tell me if they work on guitar too.
Based on the piano version from the deluxe album.
Acoustic version of the song based off of the bass riff, better to play as barred chords for the slides but works either way.
This tab is based off of this official acoustic recording of the song: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NdHayiePcfc.
This is Acoustic version on Broken Machine (Deluxe) Here is a link to the version https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NdHayiePcfc.
This is from a live performance in Berlin- you tube video.
Dom plays it with power chords mainly rooted on the E string live.
This tab has the correct tab for the chords used in the verse as well as correct chords for the rest of the song.
Easier to play chords than the power chords sequence Dom plays using Capo 4.
